---
import BaseLayout from "../layouts/BaseLayout.astro";
---
<BaseLayout title="Privacy Policy — MatchIQ" description="Privacy policy for vexp.me MatchIQ FIFA World Cup 2026 platform.">
  <article class="legal-page">
    <h1>Privacy Policy</h1>
    <p class="legal-date">Last updated: June 11, 2026</p>

    <h2>Information We Collect</h2>
    <p>When you use MatchIQ (vexp.me), we may collect:</p>
    <ul>
      <li><strong>Telegram profile data:</strong> Your Telegram ID, username, first name, and profile photo when you log in.</li>
      <li><strong>Usage data:</strong> Pages visited, predictions viewed, chat messages sent.</li>
      <li><strong>Device data:</strong> Browser type, device type, and IP address (collected automatically by our hosting providers).</li>
    </ul>

    <h2>How We Use Your Information</h2>
    <ul>
      <li>To provide match predictions, live scores, and chat features.</li>
      <li>To manage your account and VIP subscription status.</li>
      <li>To improve our services and content.</li>
      <li>To display relevant advertisements.</li>
    </ul>

    <h2>Advertising</h2>
    <p>We use third-party advertising partners including Google AdSense to display ads. These partners may use cookies and similar technologies to serve ads based on your prior visits to our website or other websites. You can opt out of personalized advertising by visiting <a href="https://www.google.com/settings/ads" target="_blank">Google Ads Settings</a>.</p>

    <h2>Cookies</h2>
    <p>We use cookies and local storage to keep you logged in and remember your preferences. Third-party advertisers may also set cookies for ad targeting.</p>

    <h2>Data Sharing</h2>
    <p>We do not sell your personal data. We may share anonymized usage data with advertising partners to serve relevant ads.</p>

    <h2>Data Retention</h2>
    <p>Chat messages are retained for 7 days. Account data is retained as long as your account is active.</p>

    <h2>Your Rights</h2>
    <p>You can request deletion of your data by contacting us. You can log out at any time to stop data collection.</p>

    <h2>Contact</h2>
    <p>For privacy questions, contact us via our Telegram bot: <a href="https://t.me/VexpMatchIQBot" target="_blank">@VexpMatchIQBot</a></p>
  </article>
</BaseLayout>

<style>
  .legal-page { max-width: 700px; margin: 0 auto; padding: 40px 20px; }
  .legal-page h1 { font-size: 28px; font-weight: 900; margin-bottom: 8px; }
  .legal-date { font-size: 12px; color: var(--text-muted); margin-bottom: 32px; }
  .legal-page h2 { font-size: 18px; font-weight: 700; margin: 28px 0 12px; color: var(--text-primary); }
  .legal-page p, .legal-page li { font-size: 14px; line-height: 1.7; color: var(--text-secondary); }
  .legal-page ul { padding-left: 20px; margin: 8px 0; }
  .legal-page a { color: var(--accent); text-decoration: none; }
</style>
